8. Hands-On Labs You Can Try

System Monitoring Lab
Write a script to log CPU, memory, and disk usage every minute.

Deployment Lab
Automate app startup: shell script + systemctl service file.

Data Movement Lab
Use scp or rsync to copy large datasets between servers.

AI Job Lab
Schedule a cron job that runs python train.py at midnight daily.

Log Analysis Lab
Use grep + awk + sort to find top error messages in logs.

